<h1 class="email-title">You're Invited to Join BrokerSync</h1>

<p class="email-text">
  Hello <%= @user.full_name %>,
</p>

<p class="email-text">
  <strong><%= @inviter.full_name %></strong> has invited you to join <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong> on BrokerSync.
</p>

<div class="alert alert-info">
  <strong>Organization Details:</strong>
  <br>
  Name: <%= @organization.name %>
  <br>
  Type: <%= @organization.organization_type&.humanize %>
  <% if @organization.description.present? %>
    <br>
    Description: <%= @organization.description %>
  <% end %>
</div>

<table class="details-table">
  <tr>
    <th>Field</th>
    <th>Value</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Organization</td>
    <td><%= @organization.name %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Invited By</td>
    <td><%= @inviter.full_name %> (<%= @inviter.email %>)</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Your Email</td>
    <td><%= @user.email %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Invitation Date</td>
    <td><%= Time.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<a href="<%= root_url %>" class="btn">Accept Invitation</a>

<div class="email-divider"></div>

<p class="email-text">
  BrokerSync is a comprehensive insurance brokerage management platform that helps organizations streamline their insurance operations, manage applications, and collaborate effectively.
</p>

<p class="email-text">
  <strong>What you can do with BrokerSync:</strong>
</p>

<ul class="email-text">
  <li>Manage motor insurance applications</li>
  <li>Track application status and updates</li>
  <li>Collaborate with team members</li>
  <li>Generate reports and analytics</li>
  <li>Manage client relationships</li>
</ul>

<p class="email-text">
  If you have any questions about this invitation, please contact <%= @inviter.full_name %> directly or reach out to our support team.
</p>

<p class="email-text">
  Welcome to BrokerSync!<br>
  The BrokerSync Team
</p>